<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA522_11_SU_0008_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_11_su.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_11_su_0008">
    <div class="scroll_page">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 4">
          <span class="blue line" lang="y">확인하고 정리해요</span>
          <span lang="y">공부한 내용을 확인해요</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="title type2 jgjd_4_sub_title">
        <h2>
          <div class="title_row">
            <span class="nemo_blank"></span>
            <span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center align_start">

          <div class="tag1">분모는 그대로 쓰고, 분자에 자연수를 곱하여 계산해요.</div>
          <div class="tag2">분자는 분자끼리, 분모는<br />
            분모끼리 곱하여 계산해요.</div>
          <div class="container flex gap_20">
            <div class="box flex justify_center dir_col f32b gap_16">
              <div class="flex justify_center">(분수)×(자연수)</div>

              <div class="flex align_center gap_0 m_auto mt_20">
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </span>
                <span>&times;3</span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    2&times;
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>6</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </span>
              </div>

              <div class="flex align_center m_auto bg">
                <span class="mixed_fraction">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <span>4</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
                <span>&times;5</span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>5</span>
                  <span>4</span>
                </span>
                <span>&times;5</span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>25</span>
                  <span>4</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span>6</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>4</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="f20b text_center">대분수를 가분수로 나타내어 계산해요.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="box flex justify_center dir_col f32b">
              <div class="flex justify_center">(자연수)×(분수)</div>

              <div class="flex align_center gap_0 m_auto">
                <span>4&times;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span> 4&times;3 </span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>12</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span>2</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
              </div>

              <div class="flex align_center gap_0 m_auto">
                <span> 2&times; </span>
                <span>1</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>5</span>
                  <span>6</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="relative">
                  2

                  <span class="division_1">
                    <span>1</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
                &times;
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="11" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span class="division_2">
                    <span>1</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>6</span>
                  

                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>11</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span>3</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="box flex justify_center dir_col f32b">
              <div class="flex justify_center">(진분수)×(진분수)</div>

              <div class="flex align_center gap_0 m_auto">
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>9</span>
                </span>
                <span>&times;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>4</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span> 2&times;4 </span>
                  <span> 9&times;5 </span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>

                <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap flex align_center">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(8)/(45)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                  <!-- 분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2) -->
                  <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 -->
                  <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                  <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                  <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="box flex justify_center dir_col f32b">
              <div class="flex justify_center"> (대분수)×(대분수)</div>

              <div class="flex align_center gap_0 m_auto">
                <span>1</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </span>
                <span>&times;</span>
                <span>2</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>2</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>10</span>
                  <span class="division_1">
                    <span>5</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </span>
                <span>&times;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="5" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span class="division_2">
                    <span>1</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>2</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>25</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <span>3</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>4</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area relative">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>